ustly"]},{"trad":"攀誣陷害","simp":"攀诬陷害","pinyin":"pan1 wu1 xian4 hai4","defs":["unjust accusation","miscarriage of justice"]},{"trad":"攀談","simp":"攀谈","pinyin":"pan1 tan2","defs":["to chat"]},{"trad":"攀越","simp":"攀越","pinyin":"pan1 yue4","defs":["to climb over","to get over (difficulties)","to scale","to surmount"]},{"trad":"攀附","simp":"攀附","pinyin":"pan1 fu4","defs":["to climb (of climbing plants)","to creep","to cling on to","fig. to seek connection (with the rich and powerful)","social climbing"]},{"trad":"攀附權貴","simp":"攀附权贵","pinyin":"pan1 fu4 quan2 gui4","defs":["to cling to the powerful and rich (idiom); social climbing"]},{"trad":"攀高枝","simp":"攀高枝","pinyin":"pan1 gao1 zhi1","defs":["(coll.) to try to improve one's social standing by marrying or affiliating with people of higher status"]},{"trad":"攀高枝兒","simp":"攀高枝儿","pinyin":"pan1 gao1 zhi1 r5","defs":["erhua form of 攀高枝[pan1 gao1 zhi1]"]},{"trad":"攀高結貴","simp":"攀高结贵","pinyin":"pan1 gao1 jie2 gui4","defs":["lit. to cling to the high, connect to the rich (idiom); to try to attach oneself to the rich and powerful","social climbing"]},{"trad":"攀龍附鳳","simp":"攀龙附凤","pinyin":"pan1 long2 fu4 feng4","defs":["see 扳龍附鳳|扳龙附凤[ban1 long2 fu4 feng4]"]}]